description:
Amp up your in-game plays by injecting new beats into classic League of Legends tunes. Warsongs is a new collection of remixed songs to accompany your competitive climb during the 2016 Season, and it's yours to download below.  If youre queueing up in ranked, you should be queuing up Warsongs.

Download the album here: http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/site/warsongs/

1. Piercing Light (Mako Remix)
2. Edge of Infinity (Minnesota Remix)
3. Welcome to Planet Urf (Jauz Remix)
4. PROJECT: Yi (Vicetone Remix)
5. Flash Funk (Marshmello Remix)
6. Let The Games Begin (Hyper Potions Remix)
7. Worlds Collide (Arty Remix)
8. The Glory (James Egbert Remix)
9. The Boy Who Shattered Time (MitiS Remix)
10. Lucidity (Dan Negovan Remix)
11. Silver Scrapes (ProtoShredanoid Remix)

Listen to the other League of Legends inspired albums here:

Pentakill: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oUiOylPbfV0&list=PLbAFXJC0J5Gb9hzEYU5buZd4udIuIUheP&index=1

Music of League of Legends Vol. 1: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8aluBPpzCHc&list=PLbAFXJC0J5Gae5_5P4coPFJqSpj8EVeN7
